ratings.en: There's No Paradise for You to Escape To
You Talented Ones Will Be Slaves to Your Talent
The Number of People Needed to Support One Person
Being Incomplete Means You Have the Potential... to Grow Into an Infinite Number of Things
I Will Be Your Unchanging Truth
Don't Be Defeated, Not by Fate nor Loneliness...
Stars Don't Disappear. They'll Be Seen One Day Again.
You Always Let Me Know That I'm Also a Flower
No One Is Courageous... Only Those Who Muster Courage...
Let's Hurry Our Steps So That Bad Luck Can't Catch Up
The Stars Are Shining for You
Life is... a process of breaking through the limits
